bookreader-desc: ʻO BookReader he hāmeʻa no ka heluhelu ʻana o ka palapala PDF/DjVu e like me ka puke mai nā kahua pūnaewele wikimedia.
byurl-placeholder: E kikokiko i ka loulou a ke PDF/DjVu mai ka papahana Wikimedia
filename-placeholder: E kikokiko i ka inoa o ka waihona
localfile-notice: ʻO ka piha pono ʻakomi o ka inoa waihona, hana ʻia no nā waihona hoʻouka ʻia ma ʻaneʻi.
no-javascript: Koi ʻO BookReader i ka hoʻā ʻana iā JavaScript. E ʻoluʻolu, e nānā pono i ke kākoʻo ʻana o Javascript i ka polokalamu kele pūnaewele a hoʻā i ka makemake polokalamu kele pūnaewele.
embebed-not-supported: ʻAʻole kākoʻo ʻia ka pāʻālua hoʻokomo iā bookreader.
